text: Safonovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Duvansky Selsoviet, Duvansky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 42 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 80 km from Mesyagutovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Duvansky District
title: Safonovka
